Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.76,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz268.134\fs22.5\pos(1016,990)}没有恶意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.76,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270.397\fs22.5\pos(870,948)}不是这些
