Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz271.27\pos(1377,6)}没有恶意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz268.138\pos(1544,510)}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz269.573\pos(1456,830)}我想说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz269.503\pos(1098,340)}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270.761\pos(76,366)}你要我原谅那家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.60,manga,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz268.365\pos(138,934)}为什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Manga End==========
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学 这本漫画借我一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想对比一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦 不过要马上还我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这边的好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}抱歉 这是非卖品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.37,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：摩耶花COS的是手冢治虫「七色鹦哥」中的千里万里子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}能拍张照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一张就随便画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.21,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：池内COS的是KOF系列的不知火舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我看看 发色就用…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去换水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有那个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正原本就是卡其色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会特别显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊原…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 部长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「七色鹦哥」的衣服得去换掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不必介意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿千
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 运动服？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为什么你会有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我的 是折木同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么折木会有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是他姐姐拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同学知道这本漫画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听我说！文化祭不是有宣传海报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海报的作者和这本漫画的作画是不是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张海报在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在会议室边上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我们去！
